{"tid":779130,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"Order Flow 理論例子分析：英鎊兌日元","createTime":"2018-08-14T07:57:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-24T21:58:16.000Z","uid":43407,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"62fb84669e53f94a00281e259f9975dd224bc5cd","tid":779130,"uid":43407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T07:57:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/notes/%E5%A1%B5%E7%BF%BC%E7%9E%AC%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%96%E5%8C%AFk%E6%88%BF/%E5%A5%BDzone%E5%88%86%E4%BA%AB-gbpjpy/2174865969462002/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fnotes%2F%25E5%25A1%25B5%25E7%25BF%25BC%25E7%259E%25AC%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%258C%25AFk%25E6%2588%25BF%2F%25E5%25A5%25BDzone%25E5%2588%2586%25E4%25BA%25AB-gbpjpy%2F2174865969462002%2F&d=7%2FGlMB%2F%2B1qOC0kvt7OfS3NU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=992c1653\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/notes/%E5%A1%B5%E7%BF%BC%E7%9E%AC%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%96%E5%8C%AFk%E6%88%BF/%E5%A5%BDzone%E5%88%86%E4%BA%AB-gbpjpy/2174865969462002/</a><br />\n<br />\n好Zone分享 :  GBP/JPY<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望各位過了一個充實又愉快的暑假。七八月是外匯市場傳統的淡季，交易量會明顯下降，今年亦反映在價格走勢上，幾隻主要貨幣兌都在區間窄覆上落。今天好Zone分享想繼續和大家介紹日圓交差盤，對上一次介紹的歐元兌日圓，價格進入Buy order flow zone後隨即向上反彈，今次則想和大家分享英鎊兌日圓的 Sell order flow zone。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/14/155512_e53985cb47e2f27ebb23b6a26b6327f3.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F14%2F155512_e53985cb47e2f27ebb23b6a26b6327f3.PNG&h=2d635666&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在週線圖上，今年年初開始價格跌穿升勢線，並出現Lower high/ Lower low 形成了下跌趨勢，在過往的價格走勢上，亦看不到現價的下方有留下強大的 Buy order flow zone可以扭轉跌勢，因此中期英鎊兌日圓仍看淡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/14/155523_9b157124d4766c7d067aba11e1200423.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F14%2F155523_9b157124d4766c7d067aba11e1200423.PNG&h=ea8880c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上圖四小時圖顯示，價格穩定地向下行，在145.25 至 147.15更形成了 Sell order flow zone，並急促跌穿在 143附近的支持，顯示在該區間內買賣單子出現很大的失衡。若價格在短期內重回145.25至 147.15的交易區間，亦會趨近下跌趨勢線，值得我們加倍注視。"},{"pid":"abb0e191ef1d36b2746bcfcf61e938dc48694233","tid":779130,"uid":132524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T09:55:50.000Z","msg":"8月真係難搵食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc990a787b6e739c3f5e00baf95ea606de5d045f","tid":779130,"uid":43407,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"abb0e191ef1d36b2746bcfcf61e938dc48694233","tid":779130,"uid":132524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T09:55:50.000Z","msg":"8月真係難搵食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T17:33:04.000Z","msg":"要有耐性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99aaa286b1eb8a70a80c4466b4fe4cd7384e59ee","tid":779130,"uid":43407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T21:58:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/notes/%E5%A1%B5%E7%BF%BC%E7%9E%AC%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%96%E5%8C%AFk%E6%88%BF/%E5%A5%BDzone%E5%88%86%E4%BA%AB-gbpjpy/2204462853168980/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fnotes%2F%25E5%25A1%25B5%25E7%25BF%25BC%25E7%259E%25AC%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%258C%25AFk%25E6%2588%25BF%2F%25E5%25A5%25BDzone%25E5%2588%2586%25E4%25BA%25AB-gbpjpy%2F2204462853168980%2F&d=7%2FGlMB%2F%2B1qOC0kvt7OfS3NU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=0c0bcb41\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/notes/%E5%A1%B5%E7%BF%BC%E7%9E%AC%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%96%E5%8C%AFk%E6%88%BF/%E5%A5%BDzone%E5%88%86%E4%BA%AB-gbpjpy/2204462853168980/</a>"}]}